dream: I am in a large cave and a man says that he will explain everything.  he instructs me to put on a grey pair of his shoes. they are like tennis shoes. I watch him as he puts a container of amber on a shelf in a large clay wall.  then he starts to inscribe some symbols in the clay.
interpretation:
Dream interpretation is subjective and can vary depending on personal experiences and emotions. However, I can offer some possible interpretations for your dream:

1. Exploration and Guidance: The large cave symbolizes a deeper aspect of your subconscious mind or unknown parts of your psyche. The man represents a wise and authoritative figure who is guiding you through this exploration. Putting on his shoes may suggest stepping into his perspective or adopting his wisdom to understand the intricate aspects of your own mind.

2. Knowledge and Wisdom: The container of amber on the shelf could symbolize knowledge or experiences that are preserved and valuable. The act of the man inscribing symbols in the clay wall represents the transfer of wisdom or information to you. This may indicate that you are seeking knowledge or insights in your waking life and someone is offering valuable guidance or information.

3. Transformation and Growth: The grey color of the shoes may represent neutrality or a blending of opposites. It could symbolize a transformational phase in your life where you are integrating different aspects of your personality or beliefs. The symbols being inscribed in the clay wall may signify personal growth and the process of becoming more aware of the subconscious patterns or emotions that impact your life.

Overall, this dream suggests that you may be on a journey of self-discovery and seeking guidance or knowledge from an authoritative figure. It highlights the importance of understanding your own subconscious mind and integrating different aspects of your personality for personal growth. These interpretations are just possibilities, and it's essential to reflect on your own feelings and experiences to find the most fitting meaning for your dream.
title: The Mystical Cave Encounter: Unveiling Secrets with the Grey-Clad Guide

interpretation:
Dreams involving horses running on the road can have different interpretations depending on the context and emotions experienced during the dream. Here are a few possible meanings:

1. Freedom and power: Horses are symbols of freedom, strength, and power. Seeing horses running on the road in your dream might indicate a desire for these qualities in your waking life. It may suggest that you are seeking more freedom or power in a particular situation or decision.

2. Uncontrolled energy: If the horses in your dream are running wildly and uncontrollably, it could signify pent-up energy or emotions. You may feel overwhelmed or out of control in some aspect of your life. This dream might be urging you to find healthy outlets for expressing and managing your emotions.

3. Progress and movement: Roads are often associated with journeys and progress. Horses running on the road could represent progress and forward momentum in your life. It may signal that you are on the right track, making positive strides towards your goals.

4. Unresolved emotions: Alternatively, this dream may signify unresolved emotions or situations that require attention. Running horses could represent the wild or untamed aspects of yourself that need to be examined or healed. It is possible that there are underlying emotions or challenges that you need to address in order to move forward.

It is important to note that dream interpretation is subjective, and the specific details and emotions of the dream should be considered for a more accurate analysis.
title: Galactic Equines Glide on Celestial Highway

dream:
My Mom, who passed away years ago, was alive in this dream. She was working at a Dunkin Donuts even though she was a Military officer during her lifetime. She had an ex come back into her life who treated her horribly, even though there was someone there who would have loved her but she just regarded him as a friend. It hurt me to see someone treat her badly, but there was nothing I could do.
I had an old apartment that I didn't live in, but kept a whole bunch of junk in. I never paid the rent on it so it was finally up for eviction and me, my Mom and her new boyfriend went to the apartment to clean it out. There was nothing there that I wanted to keep except my childhood teddy bears that were kept safe high on a shelf. Everything else was dirty and smelly. I took the teddy bears off the shelf and left the apartment behind.
interpretation:
This dream appears to be a reflection of your emotions and unresolved feelings regarding your late mother, as well as elements of your own life. 

The presence of your mother working at Dunkin Donuts, despite being a Military officer during her lifetime, may suggest that you are envisioning a different or unexpected version of her in this dream. This could represent a desire for her presence or a need for her comfort in your life, even if it is in an unconventional form. 

The re-emergence of an ex who treated her poorly may symbolize unresolved issues or trauma from the past that still affect you. It could also represent a fear of history repeating itself, where you feel helpless and unable to protect your mother from harm. This could be a reflection of your longing for justice and a healthier relationship for her.

The old apartment filled with junk represents aspects of your past or your subconscious mind that you have neglected or left behind. The fact that you did not pay rent and the apartment was up for eviction may indicate a sense of neglect or abandonment in your own life. 

The childhood teddy bears that you choose to keep safe high on a shelf symbolize sentimental and cherished memories from your past. Although everything else in the apartment was deemed unimportant, these bears hold emotional significance and represent a connection to your innocence and comfort. 

Overall, this dream suggests that you may still be processing the loss of your mother and the unresolved feelings associated with her departure. It may also reflect your own personal struggles with neglect or abandonment in certain aspects of your life.
title: Revealing Scars: A Dunkin Donuts Encounter, Lost Love & Abandoned Memories

dream: Soñaba que me preparaba con ropa para salir de vieje y mi esposa me ayudaba y luego estaba en el aeropuerto a punto de salir pero me deba cuenta que me faltaba mi edificación.
interpretation:
En este sueño, el hecho de prepararte con ropa para un viaje simboliza una preparación emocional o mental para un nuevo comienzo o aventura en tu vida. El apoyo de tu esposa indica que tienes un sistema de apoyo sólido en tu vida para enfrentar los desafíos que puedan surgir.

Sin embargo, darte cuenta en el aeropuerto de que falta tu edificación sugiere que puede haber alguna inseguridad o falta de preparación en relación con tus metas a largo plazo o en la construcción de tu futuro. Puede que sientas que aún te faltan los cimientos necesarios para lograr tus objetivos o que te falta algún elemento importante para llevar a cabo tus planes.

Este sueño podría ser una señal para que evalúes y reflexiones sobre tus proyectos, asegurándote de tener las bases sólidas necesarias para alcanzar tus metas y enfrentar los obstáculos que puedan surgir en tu camino. Es posible que necesites analizar y planificar más detalladamente antes de embarcarte en nuevas empresas o aventuras.
title: Missing Passport: A Dream of Travel Preparations and a Forgotten Essential
